{"tid":1052778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★教育局防止自殺講座 變「大灣區樓市全攻略課程」教師入會有Starbucks優惠券​","createTime":"2019-03-08T14:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T15:09:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dccc1ec2c82386fd1d963a57ba67d413aced16f7","tid":1052778,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2528272/org/e322ead8e6173472225c87a7bbf7627d.jpg/XIZchzjy1-Co1PKitnuYVuVhRHYsz0c-BP4t9gT-LfY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2528272%2Forg%2Fe322ead8e6173472225c87a7bbf7627d.jpg%2FXIZchzjy1-Co1PKitnuYVuVhRHYsz0c-BP4t9gT-LfY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b6ca6670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>教聯會資料套放座位上 入會有Starbucks優惠券​</strong><br />\n<br />\n其中，在中華基督教會方潤華小學舉辦的講座，由香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會負責，主題為「自殺危機評估與初步介入」，現場有約200位老師出席。《香港01》接獲讀者投訴指，有參與老師步入禮堂時，發現現場每個座位擺放多份教聯會宣傳單張，包括入會申請表、教聯會教師俱樂部「T club」舉辦的「大灣區樓市全攻略課程」單張、教聯報、福利單張等。<br />\n<br />\n講座開始後，教聯代表在大會主持邀請上台發言，期間大肆宣傳教聯會，並在現場招收會員，內容與講座主題無關，歷時約15分鐘。有老師感到不滿，「點解要聽教聯講咁耐嘢？」兩小時講座完結後，教聯隨即在現場收表，目測至少有20名教師交表，並即場獲贈Starbucks優惠券。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2528170/org/2158c3c6848e132e5e9f54ee9c32d030.jpg/BK7V3DaY44BLjrSIQp6I0B_iYDWnsgBLjENt-IxDbfg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2528170%2Forg%2F2158c3c6848e132e5e9f54ee9c32d030.jpg%2FBK7V3DaY44BLjrSIQp6I0B_iYDWnsgBLjENt-IxDbfg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=35092335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f29721343242420f4c8ddbc5cd617895dfa516f","tid":1052778,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/303958/%E6%95%99%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E7%96%91%E9%A8%8E%E5%8A%AB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%80%E9%98%B2%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E8%AC%9B%E5%BA%A7-%E6%8B%9B%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%A5%E6%9